        "custom_background_color": false,
        "heading": "<h2>We Exist to Give Generously</h2>",
        "richtext": "<p>We give at least 10 percent of profits to nonprofit partners each year, and as part of this giving, about 12% of annual giving is employee-driven, meaning every Simple Modern employee helps determine where our impact is felt.<br/></p><p>During the last eight years, we've partnered with and helped impact more than 100 nonprofits and we've donated more than $6 million. Giving is why we exist, and we're both humbled and proud to be able to impact the communities we serve in a meaningful way.</p>"
