        "background_color": "#e2e2db",
        "custom_background_color": false,
        "heading": "<h2>Who We Are</h2>",
        "richtext": "<p>Simple Modern exists to give generously. As a leading drinkware and consumer goods company, Simple Modern gives at least 10% of annual profits to communities around the world, equally millions in donations since the company’s founding in 2015. The Oklahoma-owned company offers premium quality products and unique styles for adults and kids at generous prices. Mission-driven and values-based, Simple Modern has grown into a category leader for retail partners Amazon, Target, Sam’s Club and Walmart, serving customers in all 50 states and eight countries around the world. </p>"
