    "simple_text_cczkff": {
      "settings": {
        "background_color": "#e2e2db",
        "custom_background_color": false,
        "heading": "<h2>Our Giving Focus</h2>",
        "richtext": "<p>Simple Modern focuses on five key areas of giving to determine which agencies to partner with each year. The company’s giving is centered around these broad categories: nonprofits focused on providing clean drinking water, furthering education, supporting marginalized communities, stopping human trafficking and addressing homelessness.The majority of Simple Modern’s giving stays in the company’s headquartered state: Oklahoma. Broken down, 87% of Simple Modern’s giving is local, with 7.2% considered national and 5.8% international giving.</p><p></p><p><strong>The 2024 Giving Partners:</strong></p><p>Water4</p><p>Restore OKC</p><p>Positive Tomorrows</p><p>Hope is Alive</p><p>St. Paul's Community School</p><p>The Pearl House</p><p>HopeHouse OKC</p><p>City Care</p><p>The Spero Project</p><p>The Dragonfly Home</p><p>Love Justice International</p><p>Abbott House Child Advocacy Center</p><p>Homeless Alliance</p><p>CASA of Oklahoma County, Inc.</p><p>Palomar</p><p>Guardian Group</p><p>Cristo Rey</p><p>Lilyfield, Inc</p><p>Halo Project</p><p>Not Your Average Joe</p><p>New Story</p><p>111Project</p><p>YWCA</p><p>Make-A-Wish Oklahoma</p><p>ReMerge</p><p>Wings</p><p>Christian Hands in Action</p><p>Mission of Hope</p><p>Hearts for Hearing Foundation</p><p>Leah's Hope, Inc.</p>"
      },
      "type": "simple-text"
    }
